2
00:00:04,960 --> 00:00:07,866
EPISODE 1

3
00:00:30,973 --> 00:00:33,475
I should be arriving in about an hour.

4
00:00:33,558 --> 00:00:35,811
Yes, I understand.

5
00:00:44,027 --> 00:00:45,404
What the hell?

6
00:00:47,823 --> 00:00:50,409
Are you all right?

7
00:00:50,492 --> 00:00:52,703
I was on my phone
and wasn't watching where I was going.

8
00:00:52,786 --> 00:00:53,829
This is absurd.

9
00:00:54,621 --> 00:00:55,706
What?

10
00:00:55,789 --> 00:00:56,998
What did you just say?

11
00:00:57,666 --> 00:00:59,501
Don't worry, he wasn't talking to you.

12
00:00:59,584 --> 00:01:00,460
And who are--

13
00:01:06,633 --> 00:01:08,093
You should be clearer about
who you're talking to, sir.

14
00:01:08,176 --> 00:01:10,220
-She misunderstood--
-Can you believe this ad?

15
00:01:10,929 --> 00:01:13,223
You can hardly tell
what product they're promoting.

16
00:01:13,306 --> 00:01:15,434
They've only slapped
some nameless celebrity on it.

17
00:01:15,517 --> 00:01:17,936
You're right.
I've never seen that guy before.

18
00:01:18,020 --> 00:01:20,522
Find out who was in charge
of this ad immediately.

19
00:01:21,857 --> 00:01:22,816
Yes, sir.

20
00:01:24,401 --> 00:01:26,486
PREMIUM DUMPLINGS

21
00:01:26,570 --> 00:01:30,532
DELICIOUS DUMPLINGS MADE WITH CAREFULLY
SELECTED PREMIUM INGREDIENTS

22
00:01:30,615 --> 00:01:32,117
"DO YOU WANT TO EAT WITH ME?"

23
00:01:44,254 --> 00:01:45,630
APPLE EXTRACT

24
00:01:52,971 --> 00:01:54,473
SHIN HA-RI

25
00:01:54,556 --> 00:01:58,685
Yes, Ms. Yeo. Oh, already?
Yes, I'm on my way. Okay.

26
00:02:05,567 --> 00:02:07,611
Coming through.

27
00:02:07,694 --> 00:02:09,821
-Ms. Yeo.
-What's this smell?

28
00:02:09,905 --> 00:02:11,573
-Hey.
-Why are you so late?

29
00:02:11,656 --> 00:02:12,866
Because of the mackerel.

30
00:02:12,949 --> 00:02:14,242
Take it easy, will you?

31
00:02:16,036 --> 00:02:17,287
