45
00:03:06,169 --> 00:03:07,587
-So the rumors aren't true.
-No.

46
00:03:07,671 --> 00:03:09,923
He's really handsome.
He looks like a celebrity.

47
00:03:10,006 --> 00:03:13,260
Please. The apple doesn’t fall far
from the tree, you know.

48
00:03:13,343 --> 00:03:15,929
President Kang will now make
his inauguration address.

49
00:03:16,429 --> 00:03:17,597
There he is.

50
00:03:28,358 --> 00:03:30,443
He's super hot!

51
00:03:30,527 --> 00:03:31,820
That's…

52
00:03:36,366 --> 00:03:37,659
-Hello, everyone.
-Why is he…

53
00:03:37,742 --> 00:03:42,330
I am Chief Secretary Cha Sung-hoon,
here on behalf of President Kang.

54
00:03:42,914 --> 00:03:44,124
What's going on?

55
00:03:44,207 --> 00:03:45,208
The chief secretary?

56
00:03:45,292 --> 00:03:48,336
I will now deliver
his inauguration address.

57
00:03:48,420 --> 00:03:49,337
What is this…

58
00:03:52,132 --> 00:03:55,177
"Thank you to everyone
who arranged today's ceremony,

59
00:03:55,260 --> 00:03:58,471
even though I clearly told you
that I didn't want one."

60
00:03:59,639 --> 00:04:02,392
"I hope going forward,
we will meet for business matters,

61
00:04:02,475 --> 00:04:04,769
not for such impractical
and ceremonial events."

62
00:04:04,853 --> 00:04:06,771
"I will properly introduce myself soon."

63
00:04:06,855 --> 00:04:08,148
-Is that it?
-"Thank you."

64
00:04:08,231 --> 00:04:11,651
-"President Kang Tae-moo." That'll be all.
-This is amazing.

65
00:04:11,735 --> 00:04:15,655
God, these bastards! Damn it!

66
00:04:17,866 --> 00:04:19,159
Oh, he's mad!

67
00:04:20,118 --> 00:04:21,077
Look!

68
00:04:23,455 --> 00:04:25,248
So where is the president?

69
00:04:25,332 --> 00:04:28,460
The new president sure
seems like an interesting person.

70
00:04:32,672 --> 00:04:36,176
Why won't it just go straight? Come on!

71
00:04:38,094 --> 00:04:41,681
Come on, you're just stressed
because of the chairman's grandson.

72
00:04:41,765 --> 00:04:45,602
Yes. Everyone thought you were
going to become the new president.

73
00:04:45,685 --> 00:04:47,187
That kid snatched it away.

74
00:04:47,270 --> 00:04:49,898
We still believe in you, Mr. Park!

75
00:04:49,981 --> 00:04:52,317
I think this might help you feel better.

76
00:04:52,400 --> 00:04:57,322
What's this? And what's with
that suspicious look on your face?

77
00:04:57,989 --> 00:04:59,115
Ta-da!

78
00:04:59,908 --> 00:05:02,911
I tucked the rest nicely
in the trunk of your car.

79
00:05:02,994 --> 00:05:05,080
What is this?

80
00:05:05,163 --> 00:05:07,415
It's beautiful!

81
00:05:24,182 --> 00:05:25,141
It went in!

82
00:05:25,225 --> 00:05:26,768
That was amazing!

83
00:05:26,851 --> 00:05:29,729
But who the hell was that?
Where are your manners?

84
00:05:47,706 --> 00:05:49,082
It's been a while, Mr. Park.

85
00:05:49,874 --> 00:05:54,921
Look who it is? Tae-moo!
Or should I say, President Kang?

86
00:05:55,505 --> 00:05:57,424
Why are you here?
What about the inauguration?

87
00:05:57,507 --> 00:05:59,050
I heard you've been working hard.

88
00:05:59,134 --> 00:06:01,011
