180
00:11:20,079 --> 00:11:23,708
Why the hell does Park keep on calling me?

181
00:11:23,791 --> 00:11:25,668
What things need to be taken care of?

182
00:11:25,752 --> 00:11:28,713
This is a well-oiled machine.
You're nitpicking.

183
00:11:28,796 --> 00:11:31,549
You think you're
the only smart one in the world.

184
00:11:31,632 --> 00:11:33,426
