190
00:11:59,660 --> 00:12:00,995
Marriage!

191
00:12:01,079 --> 00:12:03,373
Are you getting married, sir?

192
00:12:03,456 --> 00:12:05,291
Not me!

193
00:12:05,375 --> 00:12:08,419
No, thank you.
I'm too young to get married.

194
00:12:08,503 --> 00:12:11,130
But I'm not getting any younger, you know.

195
00:12:11,214 --> 00:12:15,760
Is it too much to ask to see
my grandson with a wife?

196
00:12:15,843 --> 00:12:18,262
Yes, it's too much. I'm not seeing anyone,

197
00:12:18,346 --> 00:12:20,473
and I don't plan to anytime soon.

198
00:12:20,556 --> 00:12:22,392
Besides, I have a lot of work to do.

199
00:12:22,475 --> 00:12:27,688
That's why I've arranged
all the blind dates for you.

200
00:12:27,772 --> 00:12:29,816
-What?
-I've put together a list

201
00:12:29,899 --> 00:12:35,446
of 20 elite, single ladies
in the business world for you to meet.

202
00:12:35,530 --> 00:12:37,657
All you have to do is show up.

203
00:12:37,740 --> 00:12:38,699
Okay?

204
00:12:38,783 --> 00:12:40,076
You made the list yourself?

205
00:12:40,159 --> 00:12:41,828
Wow, that couldn't have been easy.

206
00:12:41,911 --> 00:12:43,621
That's right, it wasn't easy.

207
00:12:43,704 --> 00:12:45,248
If I had anyone else do it,

208
00:12:45,331 --> 00:12:48,584
the entire finance sector
would be buzzing with rumors.

209
00:12:48,668 --> 00:12:50,962
-So--
-You've wasted your time.

210
00:12:51,045 --> 00:12:53,631
I won't ever go
on any of your arranged dates.

211
00:12:53,714 --> 00:12:56,717
You little brat.
What am I going to do with you?

212
00:12:59,345 --> 00:13:00,555
