00:13:16,529 --> 00:13:17,822
JU HUI-JAE

220
00:13:17,905 --> 00:13:19,157
KIM JEONG-HWA

221
00:13:19,240 --> 00:13:20,658
Let's see.

222
00:13:20,741 --> 00:13:22,743
If you're just going to watch TV, go home.

223
00:13:22,827 --> 00:13:26,831
Do you think I'm going to listen to you
when you don't listen to me?

224
00:13:27,665 --> 00:13:28,958
