225
00:13:36,174 --> 00:13:38,718
<i>It's been quite a while
since he broke up with Yu-ra.</i>

226
00:13:38,801 --> 00:13:42,764
<i>Maybe he's finally noticed that you've had
a crush on him and is ready to accept?</i>

227
00:13:42,847 --> 00:13:44,682
No way.

228
00:13:46,184 --> 00:13:48,603
What? Why is it so dark?

229
00:13:54,358 --> 00:13:55,818
Is Min-woo really--

230
00:13:57,904 --> 00:14:01,407
Attention, please.
Min-woo is about to transfer

231
00:14:01,491 --> 00:14:04,911
from the friendship train
to the boyfriend express.

232
00:14:11,584 --> 00:14:15,505
What are you waiting for?
Run to him and give him a hug already!

233
00:14:16,547 --> 00:14:18,674
Run!

234
00:14:25,306 --> 00:14:28,142
Min-woo.

235
00:14:33,105 --> 00:14:35,650
GYU-SIK LOVES BO-HUI
HAPPY 100TH DAY

236
00:14:48,913 --> 00:14:50,665
