I was doing it since they're regulars.

240
00:15:04,637 --> 00:15:06,389
I just gave them the food for free.

241
00:15:13,020 --> 00:15:15,231
Anyway, sorry. You must be busy.
I'll get going.

242
00:15:15,898 --> 00:15:16,983
Wait a second.

243
00:15:22,280 --> 00:15:23,531
Happy birthday, Ha-ri.

244
00:15:31,080 --> 00:15:37,336
<i>BUSINESS PROPOSAL</i>

245
00:15:37,420 --> 00:15:38,588
A DAY TO SKETCH

246
00:15:39,797 --> 00:15:41,674
<i>Happy birthday, Ha-ri.</i>

247
00:15:41,757 --> 00:15:43,509
